function is same as normal login but the place after SID is used.

Example:
[BayCom-1.38-DH$] 21 34 22 12 3
>
[BayCom-1.38-DH$] sajkdhfeufhndjffjdshfsdf
>

You can change password type with command ALTER SFPWTYPE.

See also HELP ALTER SFPWTYPE
